<ul>
  <li>Editing the <code class="highlighter-rouge">_config.yml</code> file to customize your theme</li>
  <li>Setup your code on Github</li>
  <li>Adding <code class="highlighter-rouge">SSL</code> encryption</li>
  <li>Tweaking the server to zip assets before sending them to your viewers</li>
  <li>Make the server more secure ‚Äì this is called hardening</li>
  <li>Create a script which will automatically compile Jekyll, send it to <code class="highlighter-rouge">Github</code>, and then copy the compiled files to your website.</li>
</ul>
